            <h2>Mission &amp; Vision</h2>

            <p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>Our Mission Statement: </strong></em></p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>“<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Seek Knowledge</span>”</strong></p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">At JGGHS , every student’s potential is achieved through the journey of seeking knowledge. We assist to decrease barriers to academic achievement through student advocacy and to promote student success through a focus on academic achievement, social/personal, career and global citizenship development. The parents, students, faculty and support staff at Trust College are committed to the pursuit of excellence in all curricular endeavors as well as the cultivation of individual student abilities in a safe, healthy and supportive environment.</p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Our Vision Statement:</em></strong></p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">Our vision is for all students to depart empowered with the knowledge and skills necessary to achieve academic, personal/social and career success reaching their fullest potential as respectful, responsible individual. We shall be a leading education provider in the integration of:</p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">(a) teaching and learning</p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">(b) advancement of the knowledge base through leadership and outreach</p>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">Therefore, we want to build upon a heritage and excellent reputation and to position to enhance our leadership role in academic program planning and public policy formulation. So that, our enterprise can unit in collaboration with other public/private universities/agencies, assist in the readiness of all learners to succeed in a rapidly changing, diverse, and highly technical era. In order to achieve this vision, we at Trust College are committed to:</p>
            <ul style="text-align: justify;">
                <li>ensure the mastery of appropriate content and intellectual skills of our core curriculum in Science, Business Studies and Humanities Group</li>
                <li>reflect upon and refine best practices in professional and pedagogical knowledge</li>
                <li>utilizing appropriate technologies which reflect best practices in modern education</li>
                <li>provide leadership in professional education</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="text-align: justify;">Therefore, JGGHS  shall be an Educational Institute of opportunity for a diverse learning community, offering leading-edge and dynamic education for life.</p>







